@mano_bonke confirms the news regarding N&uuml;bel. The Schalke goalkeeper will join Bayern on a free transfer in the summer. Negotiations were already advanced last summer and now things are finalised.<br />
<br />
The plan for N&uuml;bel is to join Bayern in the summer, train at the highest level &amp; get to know his new club. N&uuml;bel will be number 2 behind Manuel Neuer but will regularly get game time in consultation with Neuer. And when Neuer stops in 2023, N&uuml;bel replaces him as number 1 [BILD]

